Agree that the Eames interview is one pearl of wisdom after another. The pdf
of the interview is available here: http://bit.ly/bQlQ1e .

*Q: To whom does design address itself: to the*
*greatest number (the masses)? to the specialists*
*or the enlightened amateur? To a privileged*
*social class?*
*A: To the need.*

-- Nick

